    "These findings underscore ChatGPT's capacity to enhance learning experiences and seamlessly integrate into educational curricula.However, our study also unveiled challenges that warrant consideration.",
    "While ChatGPT proved highly effective, there is a recognized need for more in-depth explanations and the incorporation of graphic aids to further enhance the learning process.In summary, this study has illuminated the transformative potential of generative AI ChatGPT in the realm of Quantum Theory education.",
    "Its positive impact on student achievement, both quantitatively and qualitatively, suggests a promising future for the integration of AI-driven technologies in education.",
